WEBVTT

00:10.600 --> 00:12.000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

01:06.540 --> 01:08.000
[The Eternal Fragrance]

01:08.000 --> 01:11.980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

01:12.020 --> 01:15.140
[Episode 7]

01:46.600 --> 01:47.500
Xiuyuan?

01:48.750 --> 01:50.450
Xiuyuan? Xiuyuan!

01:54.720 --> 01:55.340
Xiuyuan?

01:57.310 --> 01:58.010
Xiuyuan.

02:01.750 --> 02:02.340
Xiuyuan.

02:02.750 --> 02:03.450
Xiuyuan, wake up!

02:25.620 --> 02:26.810
You need to wake up now.

02:27.620 --> 02:29.130
We're not even yet.

02:39.710 --> 02:41.300
Xiuyuan, wake up!

02:41.990 --> 02:43.780
That scumbag Zong will come after us again.

02:43.990 --> 02:45.180
We need to get back to the academy.

02:45.520 --> 02:47.300
Xiuyuan, wake up!

02:52.040 --> 02:52.530
Stop!

02:57.670 --> 02:58.780
Are you that dark stone?

03:02.150 --> 03:02.810
I don't care what you are.

03:02.830 --> 03:03.620
Stay away from us.

03:04.430 --> 03:05.410
Wait...

03:05.830 --> 03:07.620
I can't carry you.

03:17.150 --> 03:17.850
For me?

03:25.240 --> 03:26.620
Getting caught by Zong Quan means death anyway.

03:29.550 --> 03:30.220
Might as well try this.

03:50.200 --> 03:50.650
Are you alright?

03:56.920 --> 03:57.460
Xiuyuan?

03:58.200 --> 03:59.410
What's going on with you?

03:59.670 --> 04:00.300
Xiuyuan?

04:22.470 --> 04:23.300
No way.

04:34.200 --> 04:34.770
Xiuyuan!

04:35.680 --> 04:36.210
Xiuyuan!

04:47.270 --> 04:47.690
Xiuyuan.

04:47.960 --> 04:48.500
Let go...

04:48.760 --> 04:49.180
of me.

04:52.120 --> 04:53.130
I'm Lifei.

04:55.200 --> 04:55.810
Let go.

05:00.760 --> 05:01.810
I'm Lifei.

05:08.760 --> 05:10.690
Let... let go.

05:20.230 --> 05:22.890
No. I can't die yet.

05:23.590 --> 05:27.370
Master, save me.

06:24.830 --> 06:26.060
Could it be the Divine Tree?

06:39.960 --> 06:41.180
A disciple of Wuyue Court?

07:20.760 --> 07:21.620
Xiaobangchui?

07:41.830 --> 07:42.420
Lifei.

07:52.000 --> 07:52.570
Lifei!

07:55.760 --> 07:56.620
So fragrant.

08:02.880 --> 08:03.980
So fragrant.

08:47.230 --> 08:47.780
Lifei.

08:55.710 --> 08:56.300
Lifei!

09:00.280 --> 09:01.660
Lei, how is she?

09:04.990 --> 09:05.660
Yue.

09:16.920 --> 09:18.570
So you're all in this together!

10:05.590 --> 10:07.210
A disruption of the vital energy. Nothing serious.

10:10.630 --> 10:11.300
Mr. Zong,

10:12.350 --> 10:14.330
why do you keep harming my disciples?

10:14.750 --> 10:17.060
The Divine Tree's aura appeared in the forbidden area just now.

10:17.920 --> 10:20.450
I suspect the Divine Tree is on them!

10:21.110 --> 10:23.060
I'm taking them back for inspection!

10:24.960 --> 10:25.570
Mr. Zuo,

10:26.110 --> 10:27.690
Jiang and Lei

10:27.710 --> 10:28.780
were almost ambushed earlier.

10:29.110 --> 10:30.660
I came to the forbidden area out of concern.

10:31.320 --> 10:32.810
I didn't see any Divine Tree aura.

10:33.750 --> 10:37.380
I only saw Mr. Zong trying to kill them.

10:37.590 --> 10:38.490
Nonsense!

10:39.110 --> 10:40.780
When did you collude with them?

10:41.230 --> 10:41.730
You old wretch,

10:42.400 --> 10:43.610
if you want to wipe out Wu Guo's remnants,

10:44.110 --> 10:44.730
come at me.

10:45.710 --> 10:46.540
Leave others out of it!

10:47.080 --> 10:50.260
I came to this academy on orders from my master,

10:50.280 --> 10:51.180
Immortal Guangwei.

10:51.660 --> 10:53.610
I never knew Lei before this.

10:54.040 --> 10:55.690
Don't slander us.

10:58.080 --> 10:59.490
You're intentionally protecting them.

10:59.990 --> 11:03.140
Is Wuyue Court trying to claim the Divine Tree for itself?

11:03.750 --> 11:04.140
You...

11:04.160 --> 11:05.260
The academy will investigate

11:05.710 --> 11:07.380
the Divine Tree matter

11:07.830 --> 11:09.020
and give everyone an answer.

11:09.960 --> 11:12.330
Mr. Zong, you've harmed my disciples repeatedly.

11:12.800 --> 11:16.420
We can no longer keep you here!

11:24.990 --> 11:27.330
Jiaping, see Mr. Zong out.

12:01.040 --> 12:02.140
She's not hurt.

12:02.800 --> 12:04.180
Why won't she wake up?

12:12.710 --> 12:13.850
After you fell,

12:14.230 --> 12:15.780
the Fragrance Bond started heating up.

12:16.040 --> 12:16.900
Mr. Mo said

12:17.200 --> 12:19.060
you two were experiencing intense spirit power fluctuations.

12:20.280 --> 12:20.690
Xiuyuan,

12:21.510 --> 12:23.660
what happened in the forbidden area?

12:30.470 --> 12:31.140
So fragrant.

12:45.350 --> 12:46.210
Since it's a forbidden area,

12:47.160 --> 12:48.660
there are bound to be many bizarre things

12:50.540 --> 12:51.660
that are hard to notice.

12:59.230 --> 13:00.730
True. Glad you two are okay.

13:23.110 --> 13:23.780
Tongzhou.

13:26.990 --> 13:28.180
Do you smell a fragrance?

13:29.660 --> 13:30.260
A fragrance?

13:35.510 --> 13:37.060
What fragrance? No, I don't.

13:57.920 --> 13:58.610
Take care of her.

14:11.870 --> 14:13.810
This tea comes from far across the seas.

14:14.280 --> 14:15.380
Try it later.

14:19.630 --> 14:20.420
Back in the forbidden area,

14:21.280 --> 14:21.970
why did you help me?

14:27.800 --> 14:30.490
Does Wuyue Court have a grudge against Zong Quan?

14:31.320 --> 14:33.940
Wuyue Court is the number one immortal sect in the world.

14:34.800 --> 14:36.330
No matter how strong Zong Quan is,

14:37.400 --> 14:39.690
Wuyue Court has never taken Longming Sanctuary

14:39.710 --> 14:40.490
seriously.

14:44.710 --> 14:46.450
I told you before

14:47.630 --> 14:49.660
that I hoped you would join Wuyue Court someday.

14:51.350 --> 14:52.260
When that day comes,

14:54.040 --> 14:55.850
you'll be my junior brother.

14:56.750 --> 14:57.900
It's only natural for me

15:00.300 --> 15:02.060
to help my junior brother.

15:02.630 --> 15:03.210
Right?

15:06.060 --> 15:07.730
Go ahead and try it.

15:10.990 --> 15:12.060
Do you know

15:12.580 --> 15:13.570
what happened to me back then?

15:24.700 --> 15:26.420
Your constitution is already unique,

15:26.990 --> 15:28.900
and you were severely wounded by Zong Quan.

15:29.420 --> 15:30.260
You probably

15:33.710 --> 15:34.850
went berserk.

15:35.870 --> 15:37.300
Berserk?

15:40.470 --> 15:42.020
Does going berserk make you lose your mind?

15:43.110 --> 15:44.420
The spirits in the forbidden area are chaotic.

15:44.940 --> 15:45.940
Under their assault,

15:46.630 --> 15:48.210
your mind can get damaged.

15:50.230 --> 15:52.090
Just that?

15:52.750 --> 15:53.490
What else?

15:54.940 --> 15:56.330
What did you think it was?

16:17.700 --> 16:19.420
When you go berserk,

16:20.350 --> 16:22.380
you feel a surge of powerful energy

16:23.100 --> 16:24.420
that you can't control.

16:25.820 --> 16:26.330
But

16:27.940 --> 16:29.210
with proper guidance,

16:30.460 --> 16:31.810
you can make it work for you.

16:44.820 --> 16:45.690
There's a seal?

16:47.100 --> 16:48.940
Lei, are you okay?

17:15.220 --> 17:15.900
My Lord,

17:18.270 --> 17:20.140
once you enter Wuyue Court, I...

17:22.310 --> 17:23.860
I will tell you everything.

18:25.550 --> 18:26.250
Where's Xiuyuan?

18:27.700 --> 18:28.420
He went back to his room.

18:31.860 --> 18:33.340
Ye Ye and Gelin came by just now.

18:33.660 --> 18:34.820
They got hurt, too.

18:35.070 --> 18:36.420
But nothing serious.

18:40.700 --> 18:41.100
Lifei!

18:47.070 --> 18:48.690
What happened in the forbidden area?

18:49.860 --> 18:50.770
So strange.

18:58.180 --> 19:00.490
Lei, you need to rest and recover.

19:00.990 --> 19:02.530
Said you weren't going to Wuyue Court.

19:03.270 --> 19:04.580
And now you're already cozying up to her?

19:08.620 --> 19:09.340
Xiuyuan!

19:13.550 --> 19:15.290
Jiang, you're awake.

19:15.900 --> 19:16.940
How do you feel?

19:18.220 --> 19:18.860
Much better.

19:19.180 --> 19:20.050
I came to check on Xiuyuan.

19:20.990 --> 19:21.820
Yue, morning.

19:22.860 --> 19:24.660
Lei's energy was unstable last night.

19:29.270 --> 19:30.620
He almost went berserk.

19:30.900 --> 19:32.380
I was worried, so I spent the night

19:33.030 --> 19:34.140
regulating his breathing.

19:35.710 --> 19:36.620
All night?

19:39.620 --> 19:41.340
Lei was severely wounded by Zong Quan

19:41.360 --> 19:42.250
and hit by a nightmare spell.

19:42.900 --> 19:43.860
Given his condition last night,

19:43.900 --> 19:45.660
without timely treatment, there could be dangers.

19:46.070 --> 19:47.050
That's why I...

19:49.990 --> 19:52.940
So it was a nightmare spell. No wonder he keeps strangling people.

19:55.860 --> 19:57.340
Thanks for helping Xiuyuan

19:57.360 --> 19:58.290
with his breathing.

19:59.440 --> 20:01.730
Jiang, no need to be so formal with me.

20:01.790 --> 20:04.050
We're both from immortal sects. We should look out for each other.

20:05.340 --> 20:06.180
Besides...

20:07.550 --> 20:10.100
Besides, if Lei joins Wuyue Court later,

20:10.920 --> 20:13.050
we'll be fellow disciples, right?

20:15.990 --> 20:18.340
You two carry on. I'm going back to my room to rest.

20:19.920 --> 20:21.010
- Wait! - Lei.

20:22.550 --> 20:23.050
Lifei!

20:23.990 --> 20:24.660
Lifei!

20:24.840 --> 20:29.420
Mr. Zuo Qiu is calling for you.

20:32.070 --> 20:34.690
Good-looking people

20:35.310 --> 20:36.290
are just popular.

20:38.340 --> 20:39.100
Now?

20:47.030 --> 20:48.620
Zong Quan was absolutely ferocious,

20:48.640 --> 20:49.900
chasing me all that way.

20:50.400 --> 20:51.530
If Xiuyuan hadn't stopped him,

20:51.960 --> 20:53.580
you wouldn't have seen me again.

20:57.470 --> 20:58.690
So it really was Zong Quan's doing.

20:59.200 --> 21:00.450
He almost hurt Yue, too.

21:00.790 --> 21:02.490
Ms. Lin checked the chessboard formation.

21:02.880 --> 21:04.340
It was damaged by Longming Sanctuary's techniques.

21:05.440 --> 21:07.820
Elder Zong had been planning this all along.

21:09.680 --> 21:10.900
We were too lax in our defenses

21:11.680 --> 21:14.180
and let our students suffer this.

21:17.270 --> 21:18.210
What happened next?

21:19.160 --> 21:19.970
Next...

21:20.550 --> 21:22.290
That dark stone

21:22.400 --> 21:23.770
turned into a little figure

21:24.160 --> 21:26.010
and gave me some kind of red fruit.

21:26.400 --> 21:27.420
I fed it to Xiuyuan.

21:27.880 --> 21:30.770
After that, I don't really remember.

21:31.790 --> 21:34.290
It seems it meant no harm.

21:34.840 --> 21:37.940
It even found you the Vermilion Fruit, a healing treasure

21:38.310 --> 21:39.100
from the forbidden area.

21:49.400 --> 21:51.580
I found it where Lifei passed out.

21:51.960 --> 21:53.580
So it's not a Chaos Stone,

21:53.990 --> 21:55.050
but an island stone.

21:55.510 --> 21:58.010
Over time, it absorbed spirit energy

21:58.230 --> 21:59.770
and was able to awaken and take form.

22:00.990 --> 22:01.530
The Divine Tree!

22:04.230 --> 22:05.100
The Divine Tree's aura!

22:23.750 --> 22:24.380
The Divine Tree?

22:24.990 --> 22:26.770
Since you were able to awaken and take form,

22:27.310 --> 22:30.490
you must have gone through quite a journey.

22:30.840 --> 22:32.860
Why do you have the Divine Tree's aura on you?

22:33.550 --> 22:34.420
Can you tell us?

22:45.340 --> 22:46.380
This is...

22:48.840 --> 22:50.420
This is the Divine Tree Island!

22:51.710 --> 22:53.340
I've seen it in ancient texts!

23:05.640 --> 23:06.730
Is that strange dream of mine

23:07.440 --> 23:09.250
because of this stone?

23:19.790 --> 23:21.620
So it's an island stone from Divine Tree Island.

23:22.270 --> 23:23.140
Over time,

23:23.400 --> 23:24.730
it absorbed the Divine Tree's aura.

23:25.310 --> 23:26.620
That explains everything.

23:27.200 --> 23:28.100
After all that,

23:28.640 --> 23:29.900
it's just a stone.

23:30.680 --> 23:31.860
What a letdown.

23:33.310 --> 23:33.940
Elder Zhu,

23:34.270 --> 23:37.250
it's better that it doesn't reveal itself.

23:37.960 --> 23:40.970
Otherwise, it would invite greed and trouble.

23:47.470 --> 23:48.100
Everyone,

23:48.440 --> 23:50.180
the truth about the Divine Tree is now clear.

23:50.550 --> 23:52.180
We've been here for several days now.

23:52.750 --> 23:53.820
We won't disturb you further.

23:54.270 --> 23:55.210
We'll return to Wuyue Court

23:55.440 --> 23:56.490
to report to our master.

24:11.470 --> 24:12.380
Zhu Guangyan.

24:14.270 --> 24:15.140
Li Shengman.

24:16.030 --> 24:17.050
Zhao Mingli.

24:17.920 --> 24:18.820
Wang Zhiwei.

24:19.550 --> 24:20.660
Yin Ziduan.

24:22.600 --> 24:23.580
These seven

24:24.200 --> 24:27.290
are the ones who failed the monthly exam.

24:30.920 --> 24:32.210
There are many paths in this world,

24:32.550 --> 24:33.860
not just cultivation.

24:34.340 --> 24:35.820
Hope you find your own path

24:36.340 --> 24:37.140
after leaving here.

24:41.310 --> 24:42.180
I've outsmarted myself.

24:43.070 --> 24:44.580
How am I supposed to leave here and save Shanhua?

24:49.920 --> 24:50.490
Great!

24:52.640 --> 24:54.250
I knew our hard work paid off.

24:54.510 --> 24:55.050
Tongzhou,

24:55.230 --> 24:56.290
let's tell His Majesty

24:56.310 --> 24:56.940
the good news.

24:57.100 --> 24:57.820
He must be waiting.

24:59.310 --> 24:59.860
Let's go.

25:00.680 --> 25:01.900
Your Highness. Your Ladyship!

25:02.680 --> 25:03.100
Follow me.

25:09.550 --> 25:10.250
You guys go ahead.

25:19.030 --> 25:20.530
Good thing we passed the monthly exam.

25:20.750 --> 25:22.050
Didn't let Hu Jiaping win.

25:22.550 --> 25:24.290
Or our suffering in the forbidden area would've been for nothing.

25:24.440 --> 25:24.970
Right?

25:49.160 --> 25:50.010
I heard

25:50.440 --> 25:52.380
you're going to Wuyue Court with Yue?

25:56.270 --> 25:58.010
If you have Wuyue Court's protection,

25:58.550 --> 25:59.970
you won't have to fear Longming Sanctuary.

26:01.990 --> 26:02.660
I'm going to cultivate.

26:04.960 --> 26:05.450
You...

26:08.340 --> 26:09.420
You choked me under that nightmare spell,

26:09.440 --> 26:10.340
and I didn't hold it against you.

26:10.550 --> 26:11.730
Now you're avoiding me?

26:12.400 --> 26:14.100
Found a better backer, so you're turning on me?

26:18.990 --> 26:19.940
What is wrong with me?

26:21.340 --> 26:22.490
Why is it that whenever Lifei gets close,

26:23.510 --> 26:24.900
I feel like I want to...?

26:34.070 --> 26:34.860
What am I even thinking?

26:36.030 --> 26:37.140
Shanhua is waiting for me to save him.

26:46.880 --> 26:48.380
Tongzhou, what's wrong?

26:49.600 --> 26:50.210
Nothing.

26:52.920 --> 26:53.490
Your Highness,

26:54.510 --> 26:55.580
please save my brother.

26:56.470 --> 26:57.660
But this isn't the Yue State.

26:58.200 --> 26:59.530
What can Tongzhou do?

26:59.990 --> 27:02.180
Your... Your Highness, save me. I don't want to die.

27:02.310 --> 27:03.860
I'll... I'll work hard on my cultivation.

27:09.640 --> 27:11.180
Take this to Xingzheng Hall

27:11.600 --> 27:12.580
and find Elder Xuanshanzi.

27:13.270 --> 27:14.420
He'll take you in.

27:17.200 --> 27:17.730
Thank you, Your Highness.

27:17.750 --> 27:18.450
Thank you, Your Highness.

27:26.960 --> 27:27.900
You're willing to help me?

27:31.710 --> 27:33.690
I want to know if Shanhua is safe

27:34.310 --> 27:36.290
and if Zhenyunzi is taking good care of him.

27:38.100 --> 27:38.820
I'm really worried about him.

27:40.550 --> 27:43.140
Don't worry. I'll handle this.

27:46.840 --> 27:48.970
I know something unusual happened between you and Lifei

27:48.990 --> 27:50.450
in the forbidden area.

27:51.270 --> 27:52.450
But if you don't want to talk about it,

27:52.880 --> 27:53.530
I won't ask.

27:55.710 --> 27:56.660
I'm just glad you're safe.

28:00.600 --> 28:02.530
At the academy, you have people looking out for you.

28:03.200 --> 28:03.940
After we leave,

28:04.510 --> 28:06.010
we'll stick together just like we did

28:06.710 --> 28:08.450
in this monthly exam.

28:09.960 --> 28:11.100
If I make it to that day,

28:12.270 --> 28:13.180
and if we're all still the same,

28:14.340 --> 28:15.210
then yes.

28:24.030 --> 28:24.420
Go away.

28:37.960 --> 28:40.180
Though Yue left without you,

28:40.470 --> 28:41.420
as long as you work hard,

28:41.440 --> 28:42.770
you can get into Wuyue Court.

28:47.640 --> 28:48.660
If you can't get into Wuyue Court,

28:49.030 --> 28:50.010
come to Xingzheng Hall.

28:53.750 --> 28:54.450
Oh, Lifei...

29:01.990 --> 29:03.290
Why are there so many bees and butterflies?

29:03.310 --> 29:03.900
Tongzhou,

29:04.270 --> 29:06.250
what kind of trick is she pulling to attract them?

29:08.710 --> 29:10.860
Lifei? Lifei,

29:11.440 --> 29:12.620
why are all these bees and butterflies

29:12.640 --> 29:13.940
circling you?

29:16.070 --> 29:18.210
The flowers in my room are too fragrant.

29:18.440 --> 29:19.420
I've been soaked in the scent.

29:24.360 --> 29:25.530
Zong Quan

29:25.550 --> 29:26.970
clearly isn't letting this go.

29:27.710 --> 29:29.530
We need to practice that Demon-Subduing Formation

29:29.960 --> 29:31.730
you mentioned. No slacking off.

29:34.510 --> 29:35.250
Gelin's right.

29:35.920 --> 29:37.620
Prepare for the worst.

29:42.440 --> 29:43.580
The formation only needs five people.

29:44.120 --> 29:45.900
But all six of us should learn it.

29:46.400 --> 29:47.340
If someone gets hurt,

29:47.920 --> 29:50.180
another steps in right away. No gaps left open.

29:53.750 --> 29:55.180
Zong Quan is a grandmaster.

29:55.510 --> 29:56.450
We're weaker,

29:57.360 --> 29:58.340
so we have to be extremely careful.

30:02.960 --> 30:04.420
We're outmatched. Lives are at stake.

30:05.070 --> 30:06.250
If you're worried, you can always...

30:06.270 --> 30:07.010
We live and die together.

30:11.550 --> 30:13.900
Less talk, more action. Let's practice!

30:16.550 --> 30:18.900
Again? I've bathed a hundred times already!

30:20.840 --> 30:22.880
♪Nightmares rage before the dawn♪

30:24.230 --> 30:26.050
Go bathe again. Still too fragrant.

30:26.640 --> 30:31.880
♪Crushed ten thousand times, yet we embrace the pain♪

30:32.160 --> 30:35.560
♪Heaven sent us here, no ordinary youths♪

30:36.080 --> 30:38.760
♪Through calamities, we do not hold back♪

30:39.360 --> 30:41.560
♪With righteous faith, we seal away♪

30:42.250 --> 30:45.000
♪The perils of the world♪

30:46.580 --> 30:48.140
♪All the way♪

30:48.580 --> 30:50.660
♪From the foot of the mountain to the peak♪

30:51.080 --> 30:53.380
♪I've passed through cliffs of blades and seas of fire♪

30:53.940 --> 30:56.500
♪Breaking the seal against thousands, returning in glory♪

30:57.380 --> 30:59.980
♪The ones who make it are the chosen ones♪

31:00.540 --> 31:02.740
♪With you, beneath the stars, the sun and moon♪

31:03.420 --> 31:05.980
♪This unquenchable fervor is a wonder to behold♪

31:06.650 --> 31:09.220
♪One final battle, we charge ahead♪

31:10.350 --> 31:12.980
♪The path of light is not far away♪

31:13.180 --> 31:14.230
♪All the way♪

31:14.670 --> 31:16.750
♪From the foot of the mountain to the peak♪

31:17.170 --> 31:19.560
♪I've passed through cliffs of blades and seas of fire♪

31:20.030 --> 31:22.880
♪Breaking the seal against thousands, returning in glory♪

31:23.470 --> 31:26.160
♪The ones who make it are the chosen ones♪

31:26.630 --> 31:28.920
♪With you, beneath the stars, the sun and moon♪

31:29.510 --> 31:31.470
♪This unquenchable fervor is a wonder to behold♪

31:31.470 --> 31:32.970
This formation requires everyone to be in sync

31:33.230 --> 31:35.490
and work together perfectly, or it's perilous.

31:36.440 --> 31:39.160
♪The path of light is not far away♪

31:56.550 --> 31:58.690
Gelin! Gelin! Are you okay?

31:58.960 --> 31:59.530
I'm fine.

32:00.160 --> 32:00.860
Mr. Hu.

32:02.750 --> 32:03.420
Mr. Hu.

32:05.270 --> 32:06.530
The monthly exam just ended.

32:07.070 --> 32:08.820
Think you're tough now?

32:09.640 --> 32:11.820
Practicing such a dangerous formation in secret.

32:12.750 --> 32:13.820
Do you have a death wish?

32:18.360 --> 32:20.530
We're plagued by crises inside and out.

32:20.920 --> 32:21.940
Without extra skills,

32:21.960 --> 32:23.580
what if we get

32:23.600 --> 32:25.730
surprise exams?

32:25.750 --> 32:26.530
What then?

32:26.550 --> 32:27.490
Mr. Hu, am I right?

32:32.990 --> 32:34.010
Suit yourselves.

32:40.070 --> 32:40.620
Let me see.

32:47.160 --> 32:47.860
It's him.

32:56.790 --> 32:57.660
Lei Xiuyuan?

33:03.510 --> 33:04.690
Lifei sent you here, right?

33:05.360 --> 33:06.380
What tasty treats did you bring me?

33:07.440 --> 33:08.450
Were you behind the spirit energy

33:09.310 --> 33:10.290
in the forbidden area?

33:13.550 --> 33:14.530
What spirit energy?

33:17.160 --> 33:19.490
Mr. Hu, I'll be blunt.

33:20.680 --> 33:22.290
You've been targeting me all this time.

33:23.600 --> 33:24.340
Why?

33:25.960 --> 33:28.380
Targeting you? Have I?

33:35.360 --> 33:37.210
Maybe a little.

33:40.230 --> 33:41.100
Want to know why?

33:48.510 --> 33:50.050
Because I hate you...

33:56.600 --> 33:57.940
for being better-looking than me.

34:03.470 --> 34:05.580
Mr. Hu, I'm just an ordinary person.

34:06.360 --> 34:07.490
I care nothing for sect traitors

34:08.230 --> 34:09.050
or reclaiming my kingdom.

34:09.920 --> 34:10.620
All I want in this life

34:11.360 --> 34:12.450
is to be ordinary.

34:13.510 --> 34:14.570
I joined the academy to protect myself.

34:15.510 --> 34:17.970
If you still suspect me,

34:18.880 --> 34:19.700
you can just say it.

34:35.470 --> 34:35.940
By the way,

34:36.920 --> 34:38.050
Zong Quan is nearby.

34:38.880 --> 34:40.260
All of you stay put

34:40.280 --> 34:41.490
in the academy.

34:42.110 --> 34:43.130
Don't go looking for trouble.

34:59.920 --> 35:00.380
Your Highness!

35:15.670 --> 35:16.900
We're getting more and more in sync.

35:20.990 --> 35:21.900
Lifei.

35:23.670 --> 35:26.300
You're getting more beautiful by the day.

35:27.150 --> 35:28.130
That's because you're

35:28.150 --> 35:29.340
starting to see me in a better light.

35:29.360 --> 35:30.260
Really?

35:30.720 --> 35:32.820
I'm the kind of person everyone loves.

35:33.550 --> 35:34.610
Don't you think so, Your Highness?

36:13.630 --> 36:15.340
Smell this. Is there still a fragrance?

36:19.630 --> 36:20.260
Smell it.

36:46.840 --> 36:47.260
No.

36:49.400 --> 36:51.090
Fine. But why are you running?

37:08.670 --> 37:09.260
Wait.

37:10.240 --> 37:11.780
The fragrance is clearly on Lifei.

37:15.070 --> 37:17.260
Strange spirit aura. It's her!

37:31.800 --> 37:35.010
What secret is Lifei hiding?

37:36.400 --> 37:37.420
Why can't I help

37:37.440 --> 37:38.780
but be drawn to her?

37:40.320 --> 37:43.340
What does she have to do with my origins?

38:07.440 --> 38:09.530
Forget it. I'll focus on practicing the formation first.

38:13.590 --> 38:17.050
Once I master it and drive Zong Quan away,

38:19.070 --> 38:20.820
I'll get Hu Jiaping

38:20.990 --> 38:22.300
to tell me where my senior brother is.

38:29.550 --> 38:30.490
You're back again?

38:31.880 --> 38:32.170
You...

38:32.550 --> 38:33.650
I'll teach you a lesson.

38:58.920 --> 38:59.740
Who goes there?

39:02.360 --> 39:02.900
Who?

39:03.470 --> 39:04.050
Who?

39:11.150 --> 39:13.010
My little chick can talk now.

39:14.280 --> 39:16.340
Cluck cluck.

39:16.550 --> 39:19.530
Cluck cluck.

39:43.550 --> 39:44.260
Cluck.

40:15.190 --> 40:15.900
What am I doing?

40:19.510 --> 40:22.300
No. I fell for that scumbag Zong Quan's trick again.

40:30.110 --> 40:32.050
Help!

40:42.150 --> 40:43.780
Your skills actually improved?

40:44.590 --> 40:45.860
The academy is close by.

40:46.470 --> 40:47.700
Aren't you afraid the masters will come?

40:48.440 --> 40:48.940
Well,

40:49.240 --> 40:50.820
Mr. Zuo Qiu values me highly.

40:51.280 --> 40:53.700
Give it up. No one will find you.

40:53.960 --> 40:56.090
Tell me, where is the Divine Tree?

40:57.030 --> 41:00.130
Um, I can go back and ask around for you.

41:02.030 --> 41:02.780
Won't cooperate?

41:03.110 --> 41:04.700
Then come to Longming Sanctuary with me!

41:21.840 --> 41:22.380
Xiuyuan!

41:23.070 --> 41:24.010
Perfect timing.

41:24.470 --> 41:26.220
I'll take you back

41:26.720 --> 41:28.420
and find out where that traitor is hiding.

41:29.320 --> 41:29.780
Go now.

41:35.990 --> 41:39.260
Such feeble skills. You think you can stop me?

41:43.280 --> 41:44.420
I'll destroy your spirit meridians

41:44.840 --> 41:46.420
and dive into your sea of mind.

41:46.760 --> 41:48.780
Then I'll find the Divine Tree!

41:52.700 --> 41:54.820
Let... let her go.

42:09.590 --> 42:12.650
Cunning and sly. Might as well dig those eyes out!

42:28.920 --> 42:29.700
Spirit Slay!

42:42.200 --> 42:43.020
[The Eternal Fragrance]

42:43.020 --> 42:44.720
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

42:57.500 --> 43:01.020
♪The warmth within my arms♪

43:01.180 --> 43:04.700
♪I can no longer hold on to♪

43:04.820 --> 43:08.340
♪In the cold night, how can I♪

43:08.460 --> 43:11.940
♪Keep you warm until sunrise?♪

43:11.940 --> 43:15.580
♪My heartbeat freezes♪

43:15.980 --> 43:19.260
♪I can no longer tell you♪

43:19.380 --> 43:22.900
♪Looking you in the eyes, I cannot♪

43:22.940 --> 43:25.940
♪Utter that line♪

43:26.100 --> 43:28.140
♪Knowing love and hate♪

43:28.220 --> 43:32.620
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

43:33.340 --> 43:35.420
♪I still linger on♪

43:35.580 --> 43:39.860
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

43:40.020 --> 43:44.540
♪Last night's stars cast faint glimmers♪

43:44.620 --> 43:48.140
♪But we thought nothing of it♪

43:48.220 --> 43:51.660
♪With a heartbroken cry♪

43:51.940 --> 43:55.180
♪I wish you well♪

43:55.340 --> 43:57.060
♪Knowing right and wrong♪

43:57.220 --> 44:01.900
♪Black and gray are all illusions♪

44:02.500 --> 44:04.580
♪You're still screaming♪

44:04.740 --> 44:09.220
♪Running relentlessly without regret♪

44:09.340 --> 44:13.820
♪The storm looms, yet the wind stand in its way♪

44:14.060 --> 44:17.020
♪A final farewell left on the cliff♪

44:17.140 --> 44:19.020
♪Leaping straight into♪

44:19.140 --> 44:23.900
♪That heartbreaking past♪

44:24.140 --> 44:27.660
♪Just to keep you safe♪

44:34.100 --> 44:37.420
♪My breath is about to stop♪

44:37.540 --> 44:41.060
♪Those hands can no longer hold yours♪

44:41.180 --> 44:44.620
♪Through the future snow, wind, and fog♪

44:44.780 --> 44:47.980
♪Who will be there by your side?♪

44:48.100 --> 44:51.820
♪I smile as it ends♪

44:51.980 --> 44:55.620
♪Afraid that you might cry for me♪

44:55.820 --> 44:59.220
♪Quietly, I turn into a sky lantern♪

44:59.380 --> 45:02.500
♪To light your way through the night♪

45:02.580 --> 45:04.620
♪Knowing love and hate♪

45:04.700 --> 45:09.100
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

45:09.860 --> 45:11.900
♪I still linger on♪

45:12.060 --> 45:16.340
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

45:16.500 --> 45:21.020
♪The storm looms, yet I stand in its way♪

45:21.100 --> 45:24.300
♪Torn inside, still I burn bright♪

45:24.500 --> 45:26.460
♪With the light from my fingertips♪

45:26.540 --> 45:30.940
♪I build a paradise♪

45:31.100 --> 45:34.580
♪To wander with you♪
